Package: pubertyplot
Type: Package
Title: pubertyplot
Version: 1.3
Date: 2020-08-06
Author: Jeroen Ooms, Stef van Buuren
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Description: Packaged up version of the puberty plot webapp. Provides
    functions and reference data to plot Tanner pubertal stage
    measurements against the Dutch 1997 references and to express
    them as standard deviation scores.
